<h3>How Does It Work?</h3>
<ul>
  <li>Books are arranged by Library of Congress call numbers.
  <li>Thickness of the book is based on page count.
  <li>Length is proportionate to actual length.
  <li>Serials are indicated by issues bound together (<a href="https://search.library.brown.edu/browse/b3491476">example</a>)
  <li>DVDs and CDs are visualized in cases (<a href="https://search.library.brown.edu/browse/b5386010">example</a>)
</ul>

